k=USA Today \n |authorlink=Whitney Matheson \n |publisher=Gannett Company \n |accessdate=June 14, 2014 \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420134434/http://www.usatoday.com/story/popcandy/2014/04/14/clarence-cartoon-network/7694977/\n |archivedate=April 20, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Milligan 2012\">{{cite journal\n |author=Milligan, Mercedes \n |url=http://www.animationmagazine.net/tv/cartoon-network-greenlights-clarence/ \n |title=Cartoon Network Greenlights ''Clarence'' \n |work=Animation Magazine \n |date=December 13, 2012 \n |issn=1041-617X \n |accessdate=June 14, 2014 \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006072229/http://www.animationmagazine.net/tv/cartoon-network-greenlights-clarence/\n |archivedate=October 6, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Milligan 2014a\">{{cite journal\n |author=Milligan, Mercedes \n |date=April\u2013May 2014 \n |url=http://www.animationmagazine.net/tv/cns-new-bundle-of-joy/ \n |title=CN's New Bundle of Joy \n |work=Animation Magazine \n |volume=28 \n |issue=4 \n |pages=20\u201321 \n |issn=1041-617X \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724010555/http://www.animationmagazine.net/tv/cns-new-bundle-of-joy/\n |archivedate=July 24, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Milligan 2014b\">{{cite journal\n |author=Milligan, Mercedes \n |date=September 22, 2014 \n |url=http://www.animationmagazine.net/events/cartoon-network-plans-surprise-packed-nycc-panel/ \n |title=Cartoon Network Plans Surprise-Packed NYCC Panel \n |work=Animation Magazine \n |issn=1041-617X \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006123416/http://www.animationmagazine.net/events/cartoon-network-plans-surprise-packed-nycc-panel/\n |archivedate=October 6, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Rusak 2014\">{{cite web\n |author=Rusak, Gary \n |date=March 10, 2014 \n |url=http://kidscreen.com/2014/03/10/cartoon-network-us-uk-announce-2014-slates/ \n |title=Cartoon Network US & UK announce 2014 slates \n |work=Kidscreen \n |publisher=Brunico Communications \n |accessdate=June 14, 2014 \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715200810/http://kidscreen.com/2014/03/10/cartoon-network-us-uk-announce-2014-slates/\n |archivedate=July 15, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Serrao 2014\">{{cite web\n |author=Serrao, Nivea \n |date=April 14, 2014 \n |url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/cartoon-network-clarence-1080415.aspx \n |title=Cartoon Network's ''Clarence'' Finds Joy in the Ordinary \n |work=TV Guide \n |publisher=CBS Interactive \n |accessdate=June 14, 2014 \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426234413/http://www.tvguide.com/news/cartoon-network-clarence-1080415.aspx\n |archivedate=April 26, 2014\n |url-status=live\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Wolfe 2013\">{{cite web \n |author=Wolfe, Jennifer \n |date=July 22, 2013 \n |url=http://www.awn.com/news/cn-sneak-peeks-rebecca-sugar-s-steven-universe \n |title=CN Sneak Peeks Rebecca Sugar's ''Steven Universe'' \n |publisher=Animation World Network \n |accessdate=June 14, 2014 \n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715213641/http://www.awn.com/news/cn-sneak-peeks-rebecca-sugar-s-steven-universe \n |archivedate=July 15, 2014 \n |url-status=dead \n }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"McCormack 2014\">{{cite web\n|      author=McCormack, David\n|        date=October 28, 2014\n|         url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2811728/Cartoon-Network-backs-showing-onscreen-gay-kiss.html\n|       title=Cartoon Network backs down from showing its first ever gay kiss\n|        work=Daily Mail\n|   publisher=DMG Media\n|  accessdate=October 29, 2014\n|  archiveurl=https://archive.today/20141029031500/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2811728/Cartoon-Network-backs-showing-onscreen-gay-kiss.html\n| archivedate=October 29, 2014\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Harrison 2014\">{{cite web\n|      author=Harrison, Lily\n|        date=October 28, 2014\n|         url=http://www.eonline.com/news/592555/cartoo