r the host nation United States.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ifmamuaythai.org/qualification-system-events-for-twg2021/ |title=Qualification System & Events for TWG2021 |website=ifmamuaythai.org |accessdate=15 July 2019}}</ref>\n\nAll other places will be allocated through three Continental Championships or Qualification Tournaments and World Championship Events (one each for Asia, Oceania and Europe) in 2020.\n\n===Timeline===\n;IFMA World Championships\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=330|Event !! width=230|Date !! width=250|Venue\n|-\n| [[2019 IFMA World Muaythai Championships|2019 World Championships]] || July 22\u201328, 2019 || {{flagicon|THA}} [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]]\n|-bgcolor=#cedff2\n| [[2020 IFMA World Muaythai Championships|2020 World Championships]]<sup>'''1'''</sup> || TBA 2020 || {{flagicon|UAE}} [[Abu Dhabi]], [[United Arab Emirates]]\n|}\n;Continental Championships\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=330|Event !! width=230|Date !! width=250|Venue\n|-bgcolor=#cedff2\n| [[Arafura Games|2019 Arafura Games]]<sup>'''2'''</sup> || April 28\u2013May 2, 2019 || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Darwin, Northern Territory|Darwin]], [[Australia]]\n|-\n| [[2019 EMF European Muaythai Championships|2019 European Championships]] || November 4\u201310, 2019 || {{flagicon|BLR}} [[Minsk]], [[Belarus]]\n|-\n| [[2019 FAMA Asian Muaythai Championships|2019 Asian Championships]] || November 17\u201323, 2019 || {{flagicon|UAE}} [[Abu Dhabi]], [[United Arab Emirates]]\n|-\n| [[2019 CPM Pan American Muaythai Championships|2019 Pan American Championships]] || TBA || TBA \n|-bgcolor=#cedff2\n| [[2020 EMF European Muaythai Championships|2020 European Championships]]<sup>'''1'''</sup> || TBA 2020 || TBA\n|-bgcolor=#cedff2\n| [[2020 FAMA Asian Muaythai Championships|2020 Asian Championships]]<sup>'''1'''</sup> || TBA 2020 || TBA\n|-bgcolor=#cedff2\n| [[2020 CPM Pan American Muaythai Championships|2020 Pan American Championships]] || TBA || TBA \n|}\n;IFMA World Cups\n{|class=\"wikitabl